        public Map<String,Object> toMap()
        Description copied from class: AbstractStorable
        Default implementation that will read all the instance variable names using API and get the value by calling getter method (POJO) convention on it.

        Sometimes for JDBC to work we need an extra layer of transformation , for example see the implementation in DataSource which defines a field of type @{code Type} which is enum and not a primitive type as expected by the JDBC layer, you can call this method and override the fields that needs transformation.
